		(property "Description" "The BOURNS CG0402MLC-05LG is an ESD Suppressor Diode designed to protect sensitive electronic components from electrostatic discharge events. This diode has a working voltage of 5V and comes in a compact 0402 (1006 metric) case, making it ideal for space-constrained applications. It is supplied in tape and reel packaging for easy use on automated assembly lines. Trust BOURNS for reliable ESD protection in your electronic designs."
